data.description: 1/3 Acre! 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath located in 85018. This home is situated on a 16,777 SF flood irrigated corner lot with two enclosed yards surrounded by a fruit orchard!  The home features hardwood floors, modernized kitchen and bathrooms and a huge walk in closet!  Significant upgrades include NEW 4 ton AC, new fridge, foam insulation, copper and PEX piping, 200 AMP, gas service, dual pane windows, recessed lighting.  One bedroom is ensuite with a half bath and has a separate entrance.  Great as a home office or multigenerational family. Oversized flood irrigated lot boasts block perimeter fencing, fireplace, planters, mature landscaping and 11 fruit producing trees - apple, peach, plum, apricot, citrus. Garage/shop/loft is spacious enough to fit two cars and toys! Assumable VA Loan at 2.75
